RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

98-173. Gupta v. Summit Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 97-A-1152. Reported at 82 Ohio St.3d 1401, 693 N.E.2d 805.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of the dismissal for want of prosecution be, and hereby is, denied.
